			<td align="center"><font class="lt5"><b>Ação antimicrobiana de compostos naturais contra [e]lt;i[e]rt;lactobacillus[e]lt;/i[e]rt; sp em frango após digestão [e]lt;i[e]rt;[e]lt;i[e]rt;in vitro[e]lt;/i[e]rt;[e]lt;/i[e]rt;</b></font>
			<BR>
			<font class="lt4"><i>Effect of natural antimicrobials on the growth [e]lt;/i[e]rt;lactobacillus[e]lt;i[e]rt; sp. in a simulated chicken digestive tract</i></font>
			<BR>
			</td>
